title: Britain leads International Emmys with 7 nominations
text: > Entertainment Britain leads International Emmys with 7 nominations FILE - In a Thursday, Jan. 24, 2013 file photo, Rafe Spall is seen at the European premiere of I Give It A Year at the Vue West End in London, UK. Spall was nominated as best actor Monday, Sept. 5, 2015, in the International Emmys for his role opposite Jon Hamm in the techno-thriller "White Christmas," the holiday special of the anthology series "Black Mirror." (Photo by Jon Furniss/Invision/AP, File)
